{"id":"df2e96f7-a767-473f-aa75-ab3fd6335ce4","title":"1551/02/28: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"79717071-29b9-4e33-8cad-4118e0693385","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, February 28th, 1551.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"955968e9-2f30-42de-bebb-3d15af0eecc3","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"dbc0894e-3172-4aff-8254-f46fa329849e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1a5dd9c9-c0f5-4183-a973-2369c006c60b","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":29,"value":"8a7d1da4-d906-4838-ba6c-8edf538ba860","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e64f20af-4cb1-4efd-844d-3d3a51858942","type":"style/superscript","start":22,"end":23,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"ecb8e966-979e-4883-95f1-ea6837316d54","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"9cdf5178-48de-42fb-ae4d-68134aabbcae","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6326f4e6-5ba5-4a41-973c-8d602464e6ac","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"44d3f67f-3ccb-4557-bef8-6a8e38a940bd","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"60e1634a-f3de-42be-a4c7-613e2171174c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4d0bb0d1-1940-46cc-8a08-df4941a60d1f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"c73914b7-7e85-4821-bb18-1df67a5885d2","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"c2a4326c-5a85-421f-97ab-4f412e76c2ea","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0From thy last letter I learn that thou hast as yet done nothing towards getting married. I\u00A0am not at all pleased, for it is incumbent upon thee to take a wife, and as I have told thee in writing on several occasions I do not think\u00A0\u2014\u00A0considering thy present position and all that will eventually come to thee\u00A0\u2014\u00A0that thou needest look for a dowry but only for goodness, health and gentle breeding. Consider\u00A0that to marry a girl of good breeding and good character with soundness of body and nobility of blood but no money would be an act of charity: and\u00A0that if thou doest this thou wilt be free from all fear of feminine frivolity and extravagance. The result\u00A0would be increased tranquillity within the house. As to the suggestion that thou desirest to ennoble\u00A0thyself, as thou saidst in a former letter, there is no possibility of truth in it, for it is known that we are\u00A0descended from the Florentine citizens of ancient days. Think over all I have said, for fortune has not\u00A0favoured thee in face or figure so extensively as to make thee worthy of the first beauty in Florence. Be\u00A0very careful that thou deceive not thyself.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"d3879565-ec0b-47b5-b65c-8f149effaf1c","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4a25955a-b3a6-442e-a35e-58adb51b42af","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"cca00e27-9fa3-4b14-aad6-94cdb4df7e88","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":17,"end":19,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"88166dbc-ca75-4608-b189-8c22625dc9c0","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":33,"end":33,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f1